WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.765
The GDPR module brings training unit 10870 to life.

00:00:03.765 --> 00:00:08.120
In a single area you manage consents, data-subject requests

00:00:08.120 --> 00:00:14.322
such as access or erasure —, the record of processing activities, and data breaches.

00:00:14.322 --> 00:00:19.120
There's even a public portal for people to exercise their rights.
